== PREREQUISITES ==
You need apache2, php5 and php5-mapscript installed on your system to use urlCapabilities.

== HOW TO INSTALL ==
* Download the source with "git clone git://github.com/lucadelu/urlCapabilities.git" or with the button "Download Source" at http://github.com/lucadelu/urlCapabilities
* Copy the urlCapabilities folder in your web server directory; in debian like distributions is /var/www 
* Set the path to epsg file (usually /usr/share/proj or /usr/local/share/proj )
* Copy or link your mapfile/s to urlCapabilities/mapfile/
* Now you can see the page using a web browser at the address http://localhost/urlCapabilities

You can change the page aspect choosing a different css file inside the css folder or creating a new file

That's all enjoy.

== MAPFILE SETTINGS ==
These values are required for urlCapabilities
-MAP object:
 * NAME
-WEB object:
 * wms_onlineresource OR wfs_onlineresource OR wcs_onlineresource
 * wms_server_version/wms_getcapabilities_version OR wfs_server_version/wfs_getcapabilities_version OR wcs_server_version/wcs_getcapabilities_version

